{"tid":435313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8人被控暴動罪預審　梁天琦加控襲警","createTime":"2017-10-14T07:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T08:31:33.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92caff9bf6ca4df46f22a53fe44803841be7eb7c","tid":435313,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8人被控暴動罪預審　梁天琦加控襲警</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171014/s00001/fe6c36089a2bc6f222b4111604233e54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171014%2Fs00001%2Ffe6c36089a2bc6f222b4111604233e54.jpg&h=c952a13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年農曆大年初二旺角大衝突，本土民主前線黃台仰及梁天琦等8人被控暴動罪，今在高等法院作閉門預審。據了解，梁天琦被加控一項襲警罪，本案另一被告林傲軒亦被加控一項非法集結罪。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至12月9日再作預審，案件排期於明年1月18日開審，預計需時80天。<br />\n<br />\n本案8名被告為黃台仰（22歲）、梁天琦（24歲）、李諾文（20歲）、盧建民（29歲）、林傲軒（21歲）、黃家駒（25歲）、李東昇（24歲）及林倫慶（24歲）。據了解，控方今申請修訂控罪，梁天琦原被控2項暴動及1項煽惑暴動罪，今另被加控襲警罪；林傲軒則原被控1項暴動罪，今被加控非法集結罪。<br />\n<br />\n其餘被告的控罪維持不變，分別被控暴動和襲警等罪，其中黃台仰被控暴動、煽惑非法集結及煽惑暴動共3罪。<br />\n<br />\n本案早前另涉及兩名被告「美國隊長」容偉業（32歲）及袁智駒（25歲），據悉二人的案件將會與本案分開審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171014/s00001/1507960429604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171014%2Fs00001%2F1507960429604&d=gGjHpCzvCTPN%2BEj1HoMkc54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f279c3e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171014%2Fs00001%2F1507960429604&h=77719dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171014/s00001/1507960429604</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘋狂加控到入到你為止"},{"pid":"fe1ab48fc046e8f884dc8ac504bd1159f3180fba","tid":435313,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b79fd6d9e7c33f22f330f86644db50119b02b094","tid":435313,"uid":54183,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25c8e3d0f6ec56ea9a9be26b6cf6b0e9100a4757","tid":435313,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇死條友會潛逃</blockquote><br />\nblocked"}]}